item.title: Brigitte Oelke's new path on the web
item.description:
Brigitte Oelke's new path on the web

I am satisfied to participate the future of the internet by beeing a Founding Member on THE GRID. While this stunning new service is in the tryout, I will start using it to let you participate on my activities. I really look forward to create an exciting place for you to find out more about my work and life as an artist. ALOHA! Brigitte Oelke
